291
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,680
Listen, he's not reliable at all.

292
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,320
You better break up with him.

293
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,800
What do you know?

294
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,160
