411
00:19:58,520 --> 00:20:00,800
Just pretend the candle is lit.

412
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,160
Make a wish.

413
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:12,280
I wish that

414
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:15,800
everything goes well

415
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:17,520
